quote_first: It was like the clouds lifting away from the sun. Jodie glanced at Reacher. He glanced at the clock.
quote_last: . Less than three hours to go.
quote_raw: It was like the clouds lifting away from the sun. Jodie glanced at Reacher. He glanced at the clock. Seven minutes to four. Less than three hours to go.
title: Tripwire
author: Lee Child
